Mini-SIEM Project by Tal Saban
~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~
Security Information and Event Management -
Software product that provides a real-time analysis of security alerts generated by applications and network hardware.

Files
^^^^^
Parser - Parses a log file and inserts it's content to a DB server.
Analyzer - Analyzes data of from the DB server to find security events of interest.

Instructions
^^^^^^^^^^^^
1 > a Log file comes from a security system.
2 > SQL DB server gets data and parses it.
3 > Mini-SIEM uses mysql.connector library to aggregate relevant data from the DB server.
4 > The Analyzer component identify deviations from the norm and take appropriate action.